m2mimud.command
Class Command

java.lang.Object
  m2mimud.command.Command
Direct Known Subclasses:
CastCommand, GotoCommand, IntCommand, MobCommand, PlayerCreationCommand, StringCommand, StringIntCommand
public class Command
extends java.lang.Object

The command class is an object representation the command which the user entered. It is created by the parser and passed to the system.
